**Idiotic** | Attribute
__Basics__
If the Idiotic player is attacked, lynched or killed the first time they survive and instead lose their vote.

__Formalized__
Starting: Protect @Self from `All` through Partial Defense (~UntilUse)
On Partial Defense:
  • Learn `Defense was used!`
  • Manipulate @Self's `public voting power` to `0`
